config BR2_PACKAGE_LIBBCM2835
	bool "libbcm2835"
	depends on BR2_PACKAGE_RPI_FIRMWARE
	help
	  This is a C library for Raspberry Pi (RPi).
	  It provides access to GPIO and other IO functions on the Broadcom BCM 2835 chip.
	  Allowing access to the 26 pin ISE plug on the RPi board so you can control and interface with various external devices.

	  http://www.airspayce.com/mikem/bcm2835/index.html
